<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM7.2">
<l>vaṭikko ḷañcaṉa meḻutucem malarkkaṇ maruvi mēliṉi toṉṟiṉai nōkki</l>
<l>muṭakkic cēvaṭi malarcciṟu karuntāḷ poliyu nīrmukiṟ kuḻaviyē pōla</l>
<l>aṭakki yāracceñ ciṟuvira laṉaittu maṅkai yōṭaṇain tāṉaiyiṟ kiṭanta</l>
<l>kiṭakkai kaṇṭiṭap peṟṟila ṉantō kēca vākeṭu vēṉkeṭu vēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I did not get to see</l>
<l rend="indent">[Your] posture [as You] lay like an elephant, gazing sweetly at something above</l>
<l rend="indent">placing [on it Your] red lotus eyes that are painted with kohl</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] endowed with sharpness,</l>
<l rend="indent">bending the little dark feet with red lotus soles,</l>
<l rend="indent">joining with the palm of the hand all the little red fingers,</l>
<l rend="indent">having compressed [them] fully like a baby cloud shining with water.</l>
<l>I am destroyed! I am destroyed! Alas! O Keśava!</l> 
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
